Interface Query<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The result type after executing the query
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AggregateQuery<T>, AskQuery, AskQueryAdmin, ClusterQuery<T>, ComputeQuery<T>, CountQuery, DegreeQuery, DeleteQuery, DeleteQueryAdmin, InsertQuery, InsertQueryAdmin, MatchQuery, MatchQueryAdmin, MaxQuery, MeanQuery, MedianQuery, MinQuery, PathQuery, StdQuery, SumQuery
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MatchQueryBase

    public interface Query<T>
    A Graql query of any kind. May read and write to the graph.
